New Presets are

Orc Male - Ghorbash the Iron Hand
Nord Male - Ulfric,Skjor,Farkas,Vilkas
Nord Female - Aela the Huntress
Imperial Male - General Tullius
Redguard Male - Nazir
Redguard Female - Saadia

All default presets untouched !

Will work with any mods except presets mod (not sure).Also will work with default and modded game.

When i tested mod for first time i tried female presets and i found preset that is almost identical to Saadia so you will have 2 similar presets.But that is not a problem.

Etot mod dobavljaet litsa NPC kogda sozdajote personaza.
